{"tid":1438592,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"便衣狗著黑衫捉住人目的唔係拘捕咁簡單","createTime":"2019-08-09T20:55:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T21:22:45.000Z","uid":282134,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ebea0a180e15711d6a9b50a8f5b79fce37481a65","tid":1438592,"uid":282134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T20:55:42.000Z","msg":"最大作用係想令我地擔心隔離嗰個係咪鬼<br />\n當我地開始懷疑嘅話 咁又可能會spin返去捉鬼上面<br />\n<br />\n佢呢招真係好難拆<br />\n<br />\n我覺得真係要靠遊擊唔好再佔地對侍啦 可以考慮遊擊反包圍班狗  或者整返幾回合直指經濟嘅運動再諗對策先 呢個時候要靠和理非啦 之前見有個po幾好 話將罷買行動階段性升級 例如零售&gt;死線&gt;零售+餐飲&gt;死線 咁樣<br />\n<br />\n各位點睇"},{"pid":"ead6c5dd63e0f0228434a058a8135b15748a4170","tid":1438592,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T20:57:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f4e7a2e21458053e7fde8346b882bf526420564","tid":1438592,"uid":119485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T21:06:45.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻你一陣<br />\n香港人重點日程：<br />\n8月9-11日：機場和你飛&bull;萬人接機&bull;一連三日(1300)<br />\n8月10日：銀髮族遞信「900警總」&gt;「1000律政司辦公室」&gt;「1100特首辦」<br />\n8月10日：守護孩子未來親子遊行（1030愛丁堡廣場）<br />\n8月10日：大埔遊行（1400大埔巴士總站）（反對通知書）<br />\n8月11日：港島東遊行（1300維多利亞公園）<br />\n8月11日：深水埗遊行（1430楓樹街遊樂場）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GFF4YRE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGFF4YRE.jpg&h=539785ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x9Lc7Li.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx9Lc7Li.jpg&h=8d1626e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mWUQURU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmWUQURU.jpg&h=19d78c25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xYaMsLz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxYaMsLz.jpg&h=b4f4136d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CH1PqYA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCH1PqYA.jpg&h=5a975883&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PQEdSDA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPQEdSDA.jpg&h=da0e19d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/276scxO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F276scxO.jpg&h=78ce765f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Af95J0h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAf95J0h.jpg&h=5304a0a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76586479fdcf42e0ab62b7ae9d7f12c00ee2b393","tid":1438592,"uid":282134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ead6c5dd63e0f0228434a058a8135b15748a4170","tid":1438592,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T20:57:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T21:15:58.000Z","msg":"我覺得可以 但要小心俾政府成功拖到我地 一定要升級 但可以唔洗係勇武方面升級住 我覺得而家勇武方面好難拆對家招數 反而係和理非行動有好大升級空間"},{"pid":"8c3b635e1ddea3e824f78740fac105eed0dd943c","tid":1438592,"uid":282134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T21:16:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e088a8a960cda4ecfd2fe6131b5890263179b50","tid":1438592,"uid":282134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T21:20:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7b29e0348443ebf771d1477d71449aa7100ec12","tid":1438592,"uid":282134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T21:20:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f443600e4e12a4ae1476bb12b3e4ccfbac84bad4","tid":1438592,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T21:22:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}